About our site CMC Limited Information
























CMC Limited is now Tata Consultancy Services








About Us
CMC is now part of the $100 billion Tata Group, Asia's largest global software services company with over 12,000 employees worldwide. Prior to the merger, Tata Consultancy Services Limited (TCS Ltd) was a strategic partner of CMC and worked to target the global market with additional offerings that leveraged the combined strengths of both companies.


