CMC Taiwan


In the initial stage of CMC establishment, we have emphasized on developing leading electronic components and products, such as hand-held games, and pen watches.  Nowadays, CMC not only represents as the International Procurement Office (IPO) for many well known companies worldwide, more importantly, we provide the turn key solution to customers on OEM/ODM basis. Since we have long history in the field of Information Technology, and, for strategic reasons, we have invested in many related factories both in Taiwan and China. Thus, we are able to offer you the most competitive prices, and at the sametime, without compromise with the excellent quality, delivery, and flexibility. The product lines CMC carries, including but not limited to, LCD/Touch Panel, LED display, Bare PC Board, FPC, HDI Board, Component Parts, and finished products/systems. Furthermore, CMC is equipped with a product design team who will comply with customer’s special demand for niche market. This website provides the access to the angle of our main product lines.  It is the explicit intention to express our strong desire and great dedication to look for the best long term partnerships worldwide. We sincerely hope that this will serve you as a useful handbook; you are warmly invited to check on us anytime, and find how reliable we are.











| CMC Infocomm

























